  "stem": "<p class=\"standalone_statement style:1 \">\n            <span class=\"math_expression \">\n              <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"v squared equals, the fraction with numerator L T, and denominator m\"></span></span>\n          <p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The formula above expresses the square of the speed&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">v</span> of a wave moving along a string in terms of tension&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">T</span>, mass&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">m</span>, and length&nbsp;<span class=\"italic\">L</span> of the string. What is <span class=\"italic\">T</span> in terms of <span class=\"italic\">m</span>, <span class=\"italic\">v</span>, and <span class=\"italic\">L</span> ?</p></p>\n",
